  <brief_title>Comparison of Low Fat and Low Carbohydrate Diets With Respect to Weight Loss and Metabolic Effects</brief_title>
  <acronym>B-SMART</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized Parallel Group Comparison on the Influence of a Low Carbohydrate and a Low Fat Hypocaloric 6 Months Diet on Body Weight Reduction, Metabolic and Cardiovascular Variables in Obese Healthy Women and Men.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
