  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will test the hypothesis that a LOW CARB hypocaloric diet will reduce body
      weight over six months more than a LOW FAT hypocaloric diet. In addition to body weight, the
      investigators will measure cardiovascular and metabolic variables and will take blood samples
      in order to determine whether certain metabolites may predict the diet success.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
